{
  "text": "Various materials have been suggested for volume enhancement of free vermilion of upper lip such as fat, dermofat, dermis, and labial minor grafts. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] Regarding the facts that DFG is a rife and accessible reserve in the body, the technique is relatively easy to perform, and harvesting it from donor site does not bring any serious morbidity and also has a more appropriate volume and less resorption and it is an appropriate volume enhancer with long-term clinical results.",
